inutes. Court Coverage is already 60% below baseline and crouch depth just re-collapsed — the motor pattern is unraveling now. Hammer this window before he resets between games."}]}],"final_report_markdown":"## Vulnerability\nPosterior chain is cooked — glutes won't reload, killing lateral push-off and compromising every stretch-wide recovery ball.\n\n## Exploit Pattern\n- Drive heavy cross-court to the wide corner, then redirect behind him into the open court — make him brake and re-accelerate off dead legs.\n- Work the short-ball/deep-ball rhythm: drop-shot him forward, then lob-drive deep to the baseline he's already cheating a meter behind.\n- Extend every rally past six shots — stretch him corner-to-corner, no free points, let the split-step decay do the work.\n\n## Watch Window\nNext 10-15 points, roughly 4-6 minutes. Court Coverage is already 60% below baseline and crouch depth just re-collapsed — the motor pattern is unraveling now. Hammer this window before he resets between games.","total_compute_ms":57045,"match_time_range_ms":[11033,59966]}